arts.ttl: Louie Barry on the scoresheet again as Stockport draw at Rotherham
arts.sum: Barry, playing the penultimate game of his loan spell from Aston Villa, scored his 15th goal of the season.

Rotherham will be hoping to pick up their first points of the festive period after 1-0 defeats to Mansfield and Wigan in recent days leaves them still flirting dangerously with the bottom four. Stock...
